{"tid":1760120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［落選素人不是condom］ 唔入黨就唔養你","createTime":"2019-11-28T04:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T04:03:35.000Z","uid":265546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cdde85c83683c0cc9d1796ce8f743680f698e4a9","tid":1760120,"uid":265546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"區軒琴日先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />邊個內鬥邊個就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但已有政黨想合力配票做區議會正副主席<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n素人本身已經冇政黨理，落選後如果想繼續做區就要入黨，唔入唔養當人condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，政黨以為今次贏係因為自己做得好，其實今次係贏在民意，素人自費落區幫你分散建制的資源頂住班拉票同鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n當選後就爭位上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，素人無黨派就被孤立。我不割蓆，只係唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢地咁做同民建聯有咩分別。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}